title: American Steam Locomotives
description:
Greetings fellow steam heads
Although a slight departure from what I normally upload it is another passion of mine.
I hope you enjoy this small collection of some of the finest American steam engines  and railways around.
Here's a list of just some of the railways showcased:
1.Skunk Train
2.Virginia and Truckee Railroad
3.Yosemite Mountain Sugar Pine Railroad
4.Nevada State Railroad Museum
5.Niles Canyon Railway
6.Railtown 1897
7.Knott's Berry Farm
8.Durango and Silverton Narrow Gauge Railroad
Some of the steam trains showcased are:
1.Santa Fe (ATSF) 3751
2.SP 4449
3.Union Pacific 844
4.Union Pacific 3985 "Challenger"
5.Southern Pacific 2472
6.Fillmore & Western 14
7.Rio Grande 18
8.Eureka and Palisade
9.Grand Canyon 4960
10.Denver & Rio Grande Western 315
11.California & Western 45
And many more!
All are in Hd 1080p
Credit for the majority of the videos goes to Mike Armstrong...Coasterfan2105
You are greatly appreciated sir.

Please SEED and Enjoy!

PapaPitufo
